HELLO-NIGHTMARE
---------------

HOW TO BUILD AND INSTALL

  $ gcc -DNONE hello-nightmare.c -o hello-nightmare
  # mkdir /usr/share/hello-nightmare/
  # cp hello-nightmare /usr/bin
  # cp engine /usr/share/hello-nightmare/
  # chmod 755 /usr/share/hello-nightmare/engine

